info.title: trvCollection
info.description:
# Introduction
Simple express API with 5 main functionalities.
 * Managing rowing days appointments.
 * User authentification.
 * Managing news of the website.
 * Managing user data.
 * Enabling pdf download.

get.description: Get all reserved(saved in database) and available (empty default objects) rowing days appointments for specific days of the week(defined in table rowingdays)

put.description: Change weekdays, time, amount and information of rowing days

get.description: Get pdf of the house rules from the server
Get pdf of the form from the server
Get all existing folders on cloudinary
Get all images inside of folder on cloudinary
